      <title>尽管支付应用程序兴起，瑞士人仍然喜欢实物现金</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/swiss-still-love-physical-cash-despite-rise-payment-apps-2024-02-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士央行周五的一项调查显示，尽管移动支付应用程序不断增长，而且人们对无现金社会的预测不断增长，但瑞士仍然热爱纸币和硬币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/swiss-still-love-physical-cash-despite-rise-payment-apps-2024-02-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 08:37:35 GMT</pubDate>
